---
title: Gravy Beef, Pork & Veggie Filo Pie with Cheddar Cheese
description: This pie needs to be on a picture-perfect windowsill, with singing birds in the background. The rich gravy beef and pork filling will lull you into a calm atmosphere and the roasted root veggies add a crisp finishing touch.
